"},{"b":"57.6","h":"80.83","c":"الْمَصِيرُ","d":"l-maṣīru","e":"l-maṣīru"}],"a":{"g":"There has already been for you an excellent pattern in Abraham and those with him, when they said to their people, \"Indeed, we are disassociated from you and from whatever you worship other than Allah. We have denied you, and there has appeared between us and you animosity and hatred forever until you believe in Allah alone\" except for the saying of Abraham to his father, \"I will surely ask forgiveness for you, but I have not [power to do] for you anything against Allah. Our Lord, upon You we have relied, and to You we have returned, and to You is the destination.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ربنا عليك توكلنا وإليك أنبنا وإليك المصير\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, our Lord [Rabbana], upon You we have placed our trust [tawakkalna], and to You we have turned in repentance [anabna], and to You is the final destination [al-maseer].\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"5":{"w":[{"b":"0.17","h":"0.3","c":"رَبَّنَا","d":"rabbanā","e":"rabbanā"},{"b":"1.1","h":"1.38","c":"لَا","d":"lā","e":"lā"},{"b":"1.4","h":"1.74","c":"تَجْعَلْنَا","d":"tajʿalnā","e":"tajʿalnā"},{"b":"2.6","h":"3.24","c":"فِتْنَةً","d":"fit'natan","e":"fit'natan"},{"b":"3.4","h":"4.25","c":"لِلَّذِينَ","d":"lilladhīna","e":"lilladhīna"},{"b":"4.7","h":"5.7","c":"كَفَرُوا","d":"kafarū","e":"kafarū"},{"b":"5.5","h":"6.84","c":"وَاغْفِرْ","d":"wa-igh'fir","e":"wa-igh'fir"},{"b":"6.2","h":"7.55","c":"لَنَا","d":"lanā","e":"lanā"},{"b":"6.8","h":"8.42","c":"رَبَّنَا","d":"rabbanā","e":"rabbanā"},{"b":"8.2","h":"10.99","c":"إِنَّكَ","d":"innaka","e":"innaka"},{"b":"9.8","h":"12.27","c":"أَنْتَ","d":"anta","e":"anta"},{"b":"11.2","h":"13.51","c":"الْعَزِيزُ","d":"l-ʿazīzu","e":"l-ʿazīzu"},{"b":"12.4","h":"14.8","c":"الْحَكِيمُ","d":"l-ḥakīmu","e":"l-ḥakīmu"}],"a":{"g":"Our Lord, make us not [objects of] torment for the disbelievers and forgive us, our Lord. Indeed, it is You who is the Exalted in Might, the Wise.\""}},"6":{"w":[{"b":"0.09","h":"0.5","c":"لَقَدْ","d":"laqad","e":"laqad"},{"b":"0.59","h":"1.01","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"kāna"},{"b":"1.2","h":"1.76","c":"لَكُمْ","d":"lakum","e":"lakum"},{"b":"1.7","h":"2.38","c":"فِيهِمْ","d":"fīhim","e":"fīhim"},{"b":"2.5","h":"3.36","c":"أُسْوَةٌ","d":"us'watun","e":"us'watun"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.4","c":"حَسَنَةٌ","d":"ḥasanatun","e":"ḥasanatun"},{"b":"4.2","h":"5.49","c":"لِمَنْ","d":"liman","e":"liman"},{"b":"5.5","h":"6.76","c":"كَانَ","d":"kāna","e":"kāna"},{"b":"6.1","h":"7.58","c":"يَرْجُوا","d":"yarjū","e":"yarjū"},{"b":"7.0","h":"8.37","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"l-laha"},{"b":"7.5","h":"9.27","c":"وَالْيَوْمَ","d":"wal-yawma","e":"wal-yawma"},{"b":"8.4","h":"10.47","c":"الْءَاخِرَ","d":"l-ākhira","e":"l-ākhira"},{"b":"9.9","h":"13","c":"وَمَنْ","d":"waman","e":"waman"},{"b":"11.","h":"14.12","c":"يَتَوَلَّ","d":"yatawalla","e":"yatawalla"},{"b":"11.9","h":"15.15","c":"فَإِنَّ","d":"fa-inna","e":"fa-inna"},{"b":"13.1","h":"16.59","c":"اللَّهَ","d":"l-laha","e":"l-laha"},{"b":"13.9","h":"17.42","c":"هُوَ","d":"huwa","e":"huwa"},{"b":"14.3","h":"17.89","c":"الْغَنِيُّ","d":"l-ghaniyu","e":"l-ghaniyu"},{"b":"15.2","h":"19.02","c":"الْحَمِيدُ","d":"l-ḥamīdu","e":"l-ḥamīdu"}],"a":{"g":"There has certainly been for you in them an excellent pattern for anyone whose hope is in Allah and the Last Day. And whoever turns away - then indeed, Allah is the Free of need, the Praiseworthy."}},"7":{"w":[{"b":"0.08","h":"0.04","c":"عَسَى","d":"ʿasā